  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized pilot trial comparing scheduled morphine dosing with a weaning protocol to&#xD;
      intermittent morphine dosing on an as-needed basis for newborns with neonatal abstinence&#xD;
      syndrome.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
